<HL>
   Paper Companies Still Singing the Blues
   ----
   By G. Pierre Goad
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/15/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4A
</SO>
